# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a court in pakistan on tuesday ordered the father of a scottish girl at the center of a custody battle to surrender her passport , as her father filed court papers claiming no muslim girl can be placed with an apostate mother in a sexually permissive culture .
# ::alignments
(o / order-01
      :ARG0 (c / court
            :location (c2 / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Pakistan")))
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                  :ARG1 (g / girl
                        :mod (c3 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Scotland"))
                        :ARG1-of (c4 / center-01
                              :ARG2 (b / battle-01
                                    :ARG2 (c5 / custody))))
                  :ARG2 (f / father)))
      :ARG2 (s / surrender-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (p2 / passport
                  :poss g))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday))
      :ARG1-of (c6 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (f2 / file-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (p3 / paper
                        :mod (c7 / court)
                        :ARG0-of (c8 / claim-01
                              :ARG1 (p4 / possible-01
                                    :polarity -
                                    :ARG1 (p5 / place-01
                                          :ARG1 (g2 / girl
                                                :mod (r / religious-group
                                                      :name (n3 / name
                                                            :op1 "Islam")))
                                          :ARG2 (c9 / culture
                                                :ARG1-of (p6 / permissive-02
                                                      :manner (s2 / sexual))))))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok crocodile hunter steve irwin and his wife terri have a new nipper _ a baby son born this week in a hospital near their zoo .
# ::alignments
(h / have-03
      :ARG0 (a / and
            :op1 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Steve"
                        :op2 "Irwin")
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / hunt-01
                        :ARG1 (r / rocodile)))
            :op2 (p2 / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Terri")
                  :ARG0-of (h3 / have-rel-role-91
                        :ARG1 p
                        :ARG2 (w / wife))))
      :ARG1 (n3 / nipper
            :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01)
            :domain (b / bear-02
                  :ARG1 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of h3
                        :ARG1 a
                        :ARG2 (s / son))
                  :mod (b2 / baby))
            :location (h4 / hospital
                  :ARG1-of (n5 / near-02
                        :ARG2 (z / zoo
                              :poss a)))
            :time (w2 / week
                  :mod (t / this))))
